  "extras": {
    "summary": "AN ACT TO AMEND SECTION 25-7-25, MISSISSIPPI CODE OF 1972, TO AUTHORIZE THE BOARD OF SUPERVISORS OF A COUNTY TO INCREASE THE FILING FEES IN THIS SECTION BY TEN PERCENT (10%) ANNUALLY; TO REQUIRE THE CLERK OF THE JUSTICE COURT TO PUBLICLY POST A HARDCOPY OF THE FEE SCHEDULE AND POST THE FEE SCHEDULE IN A PUBLICLY ACCESSIBLE DIGITAL FORMAT AVAILABLE ON THE INTERNET IF THE FILING FEES ARE INCREASED; AND FOR RELATED PURPOSES."
